%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20work%20bags%20for%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-backpacks-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20backpacks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-weekender-bags%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20weekenders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-crossbody-bags%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20crossbody%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151096459282z-20%26h%3D1e980f50b123836c7fe311d9d59bb4a6c6b0cde2339edcb0b6cb8db36ae8ef63%26postID%3D681ce2aca865711b0ab75b62%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftravel%252Fdagne-dover-luggage-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.dagnedover.com%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDagne%20Dover%3C%2Fa%3E%20launched%20its%20first%20luggage%20line%20last%20year%2C%20I%20was%20obviously%20intrigued.%20When%20my%20beloved%20decade-old%20suitcase%20hardshell%20suitcase%20broke%20beyond%20repair%2C%20I%20bought%20the%20brand's%20Sydney%20Checked%20Luggage%20and%20the%20smaller%20Seattle%20Carry-On%20bag.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20use%2C%20my%20takeaway%20is%20that%20the%20Sydney%20is%20worth%20the%20high%20price%2C%20but%20the%20Seattle%20might%20not%20be%20for%20everyone.%20Read%20on%20to%20learn%20about%20my%20experience%20with%20both%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a7240f63-224c-4c91-ac60-9728785f6a70%5C%22%3EDesign%20and%20specs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sydney%20Checked%20Luggage%20(left)%2C%20next%20to%20the%20Seattle%20smaller%20Carry-On%20(right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6827860f68a29290080194c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sydney%20Checked%20Luggage%20(left)%2C%20next%20to%20the%20Seattle%20smaller%20Carry-On%20(right).%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20many%20suitcases%20are%20utilitarian%2C%20I%20like%20the%20look%20of%20the%20Dagne%20Dover's%20luggage%20line.%20The%20bags%20have%20a%20sleek%20profile%20and%20are%20made%20from%20high-end%20fabric%2C%20which%20sets%20them%20apart%20from%20the%20other%20suitcases%20on%20the%20baggage%20carousel.%20This%20fabric%20is%20different%20from%20Dagne%20Dover's%20signature%20neoprene%20%E2%80%94%20its%20suitcases%20are%20made%20from%20more%20durable%20100%25%20recycled%20polyester.%20The%20suitcases%20have%20thoughtful%20features%2C%20including%20large%20front%20openings%2C%20small%20zipper%20pockets%20on%20the%20back%2C%20padded%20handles%2C%20and%20compression%20straps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bags%20also%20have%20reinforced%20corners%20and%20feet%20on%20the%20side%20to%20keep%20the%20base%20of%20the%20luggage%20off%20the%20ground.%20I%20hope%20that%20both%20of%20these%20features%20will%20help%20my%20suitcases%20last%20longer.%20When%20I%20need%20to%20lift%20either%20bag%2C%20I%20appreciate%20that%20I%20can%20use%20the%20handles%20on%20either%20the%20top%20or%20side%20of%20each%20suitcase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20suitcases%20share%20many%20of%20the%20same%20features%2C%20the%20Seattle%20carry-on%20and%20Sydney%20checked%20luggage%20are%20not%20identical.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20differences%20is%20that%20Sydney%20is%20expandable%2C%20whereas%20Seattle%20is%20not.%20However%2C%20the%20Seattle%20bags%20have%20more%20pockets%2C%20including%20two%20additional%20interior%20pockets%20and%20two%20additional%20exterior%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22387ec9cd-b6bb-4bb2-a9a6-f130afc601d8%5C%22%3EWhat%20it's%20like%20to%20use%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20a%20much%20better%20experience%20with%20Dagne%20Dover's%20Sydney%20checked%20luggage%20than%20the%20Seattle%20carry-on%20luggage%2C%20even%20though%20both%20share%20similar%20features.%20I've%20used%20the%20Sydney%20on%20about%20a%20half%20dozen%20trips%2C%20including%20to%20Iceland%2C%20a%20road%20trip%20to%20Philadephia%2C%20and%20an%20Amtrak%20trip%20on%20the%20Northeast%20corridor.%20My%20husband%20has%20also%20used%20the%20suitcase%20for%20trips%20to%20New%20Orleans%20and%20Asheville.%20My%20husband%20likes%20the%20Sydney%20so%20much%20that%20I%20am%20considering%20getting%20a%20second%20in%20case%20we%20both%20travel%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20sydney%20checked%20carry%20on%20on%20an%20amtrak%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6827878468a2929008019524%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sydney%20has%20taken%20many%20trips%20with%20me%2C%20including%20on%20an%20Amtrak%20train.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20Sydney%20is%20a%20great%20size.%20On%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20Iceland%2C%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20it%20would%20be%20big%20enough%20to%20fit%20all%20of%20the%20items%20I%20would%20typically%20bring%20on%20a%20weeklong%20trip%2C%20plus%20the%20specialty%20items%20I%20needed%2C%20including%20a%20down%20coat%2C%20hiking%20boots%2C%20rain%20pants%2C%20base%20layers%2C%20and%20snow%20boots.%20Fortunately%2C%20everything%20fit%20easily.%20For%20those%20who%20want%20a%20big%20suitcase%20but%20don't%20need%20something%20huge%2C%20the%20Sydney%20comes%20in%20a%20smaller%2025-inch%20version%20that%20is%20still%20roomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20like%20that%20both%20the%20Sydney%20and%20the%20Seattle%20have%20interior%20straps%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20which%20I%20can%20use%20to%20compress%20the%20items%20in%20my%20suitcase%20a%20little.%20One%20side%20also%20has%20a%20zippered%20cover%20that%20keeps%20everything%20on%20that%20side%20in%20place%20when%20I%20open%20my%20suitcase.%20Both%20suitcases%20are%20exceptionally%20easy%20to%20roll%2C%20even%20when%20fully%20loaded.%20The%20wheels%20can%20turn%20360%20degrees%20and%20glide%20more%20smoothly%20than%20any%20other%20roller%20bags%20I've%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20feature%20of%20the%20bags%20is%20their%20large%20zippered%20openings%20on%20the%20front.%20In%20theory%2C%20I%20like%20suitcases%20that%20have%20a%20front%20pocket%20for%20items%20I%20need%20to%20access%20easily.%20However%2C%20in%20practice%2C%20I%20find%20that%20these%20pockets%20take%20so%20much%20space%20away%20from%20the%20suitcase%20interior%20that%20it's%20not%20worth%20the%20trade-off.%20Dange%20Dover's%20unique%20design%20solves%20that%20problem.%20I've%20used%20the%20front%20zippered%20opening%20two%20ways.%20First%2C%20after%20packing%2C%20I%20zip%20up%20the%20suitcase%20and%20unzip%20the%20front%20compartment%20to%20pack%20anything%20I%20might%20need%20to%20access%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20including%20documents%20I%20might%20need%20to%20access%20quickly%20or%20my%20laptop.%20Second%2C%20the%20front%20opening%20is%20invaluable%20when%20I%20need%20to%20quickly%20throw%20something%20in%20my%20suitcase.%20I%20travel%20with%20my%20kids%20frequently%20and%20it's%20common%20for%20us%20to%20spot%20something%20that%20we%20nearly%20left%20behind%20in%20the%20hotel%20room%20while%20rushing%20out%20the%20door.%20It%20is%20very%20convenient%20to%20be%20able%20to%20stash%20these%20items%20in%20the%20suitcase%20without%20fully%20opening%20it.%20I've%20also%20used%20the%20front%20opening%20to%20pack%20my%20winter%20coat%20after%20I've%20arrived%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22overhead%20shot%20of%20the%20dagne%20dover%20bag%20showing%20the%20pocket%20holding%20a%20pair%20of%20shoes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68278a593fe8d39283661d88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20standout%20features%20of%20the%20bags%20is%20the%20generous%20front%20pocket%2C%20which%20is%20roomy%20enough%20to%20hold%20a%20pair%20of%20shoes.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20like%20that%20the%20Sydney%20can%20be%20expanded.%20This%20is%20useful%20for%20times%20when%20I%20pick%20up%20extra%20items%20while%20traveling.%20When%20I%20travel%2C%20I%20usually%20change%20hotels%20every%20few%20nights.%20Expanding%20my%20suitcase%20gives%20me%20a%20little%20more%20room%20to%20stay%20organized%20without%20having%20to%20struggle%20with%20a%20full%20suitcase%20every%20time%20I'm%20on%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20carry-on%20Seattle%20suffers%20from%20sizing%20issues.%20At%208.75%20x%2013%20x%2020.5%20inches%2C%20the%20small%20Sydney%20is%20noticeably%20smaller%20than%20the%20standard%20domestic%20carry-on%20limit%20of%209%20x%2014%20x%2022%20inches%2C%20while%20the%20large%20size%20is%20noticeably%20bigger%20at%2013.5%20x%208.75%20x%2023.5%20inches.%20The%20brand%20made%20one%20bag%20that%20was%20too%20small%20and%20one%20bag%20that%20was%20too%20large%2C%20instead%20of%20one%20that%20was%20just%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22an%20away%20suitcase%20next%20to%20the%20dagne%20cover%20carry-on%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6827858768a29290080194a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAway's%20Carry-On%20bag%20(left)%20is%20more%20generously%20sized%20than%20the%20smaller%20Seattle%20bag%20(right)%20and%20costs%20about%20half%20the%20price.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20to%20travel%20carry-on%20only%20whenever%20I%20can%2C%20and%20using%20every%20allowable%20inch%20is%20nice.%20However%2C%20the%20smaller%20Seattle's%20paltry%2033%20liters%20of%20packing%20space%20only%20works%20for%20shorter%20trips%20and%20times%20when%20I%20check%20a%20bag%20and%20only%20need%20a%20carry-on%20for%20essentials%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20pack%2C%20such%20as%20my%20toiletries%20and%20laptop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20haven't%20tried%20the%20larger%20Seattle%20carry-on%2C%20one%20Business%20Insider%20editor%20did.%20When%20she%20arrived%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20she%20discovered%20that%20it%20wouldn't%20fit%20in%20American%20Airlines's%20carry-on%20sizer%2C%20and%20the%20airline%20forced%20her%20to%20check%20her%20bag.%20Despite%20being%20physically%20larger%20than%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-151096459282z-20%26h%3D1acc33af13aab900f6d740eb10faac55c61a1e8cf7044d9fc1b7ed2971677da3%26postID%3D681ce2aca865711b0ab75b62%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftravel%252Fdagne-dover-luggage-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.awaytravel.com%252Fproducts%252Fbigger-carry-on-coast-blue%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAway%20Bigger%20Carry-On%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20larger%20Seattle%20actually%20offered%207%20fewer%20liters%20of%20packing%20space%2C%20which%20is%20frustrating%20%E2%80%94%20why%20make%20an%20unnecessarily%20bigger%20big%20that%20fits%20less%3F%20This%20is%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20travelers%20like%20me%20who%20prefer%20to%20travel%20carry-on%20whenever%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1c7697c-7be1-4e67-b37b-8db4e546d0cd%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20it%20stand%20out%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sydney%20is%20thoughtfully%20designed%2C%20with%20features%20like%20a%20practical%20front%20opening%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20expand%20the%20suitcase%2C%20and%20the%20smoothest%20glide%20of%20any%20suitcase%20I%20have%20ever%20used.%20With%20the%20exception%20of%20being%20able%20to%20expand%20the%20bag%2C%20the%20Seattle%20has%20all%20of%20the%20same%20features.%20Although%20I%20stuck%20with%20basic%20black%2C%20I%20like%20that%20Dange%20Dover%20suitcases%20come%20in%20four%20colors%3A%20cool%20smoky%20gray%2C%20deep%20olive%20green%2C%20and%20muted%20pink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250134a76-5cc1-4c10-9591-0066d67ed33f%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20Dagne%20Dover%20suitcase%20in%20an%20airline%20sizer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68276e263fe8d392836616ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20our%20editors%20found%20it%20frustrating%20to%20have%20to%20check%20the%20Larger%20Seattle%20Carry-On%20because%20it%20was%20just%20over%20the%20American%20Airlines%20sizer%20limits%20no%20matter%20how%20she%20tried%20to%20fit%20it%20in%20the%20sizer.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20Dange%20Dover's%20suitcases%20is%20very%20high%20compared%20to%20competitors%20%E2%80%94%20about%20double%20the%20cost%20of%20similar%20bags%20from%20Away%2C%20Beis%2C%20Monos%2C%20and%20Travelpro.%20Given%20the%20high%20price%2C%20it's%20surprising%20that%20you%20get%20fewer%20features%20in%20Dagne%20Dover%20bags%20that%20now%20come%20standard%20with%20most%20luggage%2C%20like%20built-in%20locks%2C%20robust%20interior%20compression%20and%20organization%2C%20and%20a%20lifetime%20warranty%20(Dagne%20Dover%20offers%20only%2010%20years).%20However%2C%20since%20I%20travel%20frequently%2C%20a%20well-designed%20suitcase%20is%20worth%20investing%20in%20for%20me%2C%20and%20Dagne%20Dover's%20bags%20feel%20very%20well%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20mentioned%20before%2C%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Seattle%20Carry-On%20just%20feels%20off.%20For%20a%20bag%20that%20reportedly%20took%20years%20to%20develop%20and%20costs%20as%20much%20as%20premium%20brands%2C%20I'm%20surprised%20that%20the%20sizing%20just%20completely%20misses%20the%20mark.%3C