iking%20to%20painful%20levels.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20combination%20of%20diminished%20appetite%20to%20buy%20US%20assets%20and%20the%20rigidity%20of%20a%20US%20fiscal%20process%20that%20locks%20in%20very%20high%20deficits%20is%20what%20is%20making%20the%20market%20very%20nervous%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20Saravelos%2C%20Deutsche%20Bank's%20head%20of%20FX%20research%2C%20said%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20a%20key%20problem%20for%20the%20US%20was%20bond%20and%20currency%20markets%20failing%20to%20properly%20price%20in%20fiscal%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20other%20assets%20were%20moving%20on%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d6beb13-21f7-4387-9822-f60fd4674b2b%5C%22%3EUS%20stocks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20and%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%20fell%201%25.%20The%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%20lost%20285%20points.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20credit%20rating%20downgrade%20adds%20to%20a%20long%20list%20of%20uncertainties%20that%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20weighing%20right%20now%2C%20including%20tariff%2C%20fiscal%2C%20inflation%20and%20economic%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20Geranen%2C%20the%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20CalBay%20investments%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS-related%20stocks%20and%20investment%20trusts%20dominated%20the%20list%20of%20losers%20on%20Monday%20morning%20in%20London%2C%20while%20precious%20metals%20miners%20were%20higher%20as%20gold%20and%20silver%20prices%20moved%20up%20and%20the%20dollar%20weakened%2C%26quot%3B%20AJ%20Bell%20investment%20director%20Russ%20Mould%20wrote%20in%20a%20Monday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSignificantly%2C%20the%20US%2030-year%20Treasury%20yield%20flashed%20a%20warning%20signal%20as%20it%20hit%20the%205%25%20mark%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20April%2C%20with%20the%20proposed%20tax%20cuts%20making%20their%20way%20through%20Congress%2C%20expected%20in%20some%20quarters%20to%20inc