Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20just%2022%20years%20old%2C%20and%20my%20mind%20was%20blown%20by%20all%20these%20financial%20tools%20I%20hadn't%20thought%20about%20before.%20That's%20when%20I%20decided%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20them%20and%20that%20I'd%20do%20everything%20I%20could%20to%20try%20to%20retire%20early.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20job%20and%20each%20after%2C%20I%20put%20away%20as%20much%20money%20as%20I%20could%20from%20every%20paycheck%20by%20living%20below%20my%20means.%20I%20checked%20my%20savings%20often%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-invest-in-mutual-funds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvested%20in%20mutual%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20bought%20stock%20purchase%20plans%20at%20discounts%20through%20companies%20I%20worked%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20originally%20hoped%20to%20retire%20at%2055%2C%20I%20felt%20ready%20to%20do%20it%20once%20I'd%20accrued%20%242%20million%20in%20savings%20and%20investments.%20It%20happened%20faster%20than%20I%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2049%2C%20I%20retired%20and%20started%20making%20plans%20to%20travel%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1b46064-3576-4283-99b8-9ec0df7a4f5c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnce%20our%20kids%20were%20grown%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20sold%20our%20house%20to%20travel%20full-time%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223968%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Chris%20Englert%20and%20husband%20smiling%20on%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681cb13ea466d2b74ab55e9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222232%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20realized%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20could%20travel%20the%20world%20for%20years%20if%20we%20budgeted%20well.%20%3Cp%3EChris%20Englert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20retired%20six%20years%20earlier%20than%20anticipated%2C%20I%20didn't%20start%20doing%20a%20ton