Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Xiaomi's%20billionaire%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxiaomi-ceo-lei-jun-2014-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELei%20Jun%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20his%20company%20was%20implementing%20a%2010-year%20plan%20to%20invest%2050%20billion%20yuan%2C%20roughly%20%247%20billion%2C%20into%20chip%20design%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20make%20chips%20of%20its%20own%20for%20its%20smartphones.%20To%20date%2C%20it%20has%20relied%20on%20US%20firm%20Qualcomm%20and%20Taiwanese%20firm%20MediaTek%20for%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2Fu%2F1749127163%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20to%20Chinese%20social%20media%20site%20Weibo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Lei%20said%20his%20company%20%26quot%3Bmade%20a%20major%20decision%26quot%3B%20back%20in%202021%20to%20restart%20the%20process%20of%20developing%20its%20own%20silicon%20for%20smartphones%20after%20an%20initial%20effort%20in%20the%20previous%20decade%20faced%20setbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20largely%20popularized%20the%20so-called%20system-on-a-chip%20(SoC)%20approach%2C%20spending%20the%20past%2015%20years%20powering%20products%20like%20iPhones%20and%20Macs%20with%20its%20own%20silicon%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-chip-design-silicon-secret-weapon-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20executives%20believe%3C%2Fa%3E%20gives%20their%20products%20an%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F1749127163%2F5167955270961441%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELei%20also%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Weibo%20that%20the%20first%20chip%20from%20its%20new%20mobile%20efforts%2C%20Xring%2001%2C%20would%20be%20unveiled%20on%20May%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChips%20are%20the%20underlying%20core%20track%20for%20Xiaomi%20to%20break%20through%20hardcore%20technology%2C%20and%20we%20will%20definitely%20go%20all%20out%2C%26quot%3B