80%99s%20listing%20on%20the%20stock%20exchange%20symbolises%20the%20success%20possible%20when%20early%20investors%20back%20long-term%20climate%20innovation.%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fswapniljain89%2Fstatus%2F1919636042405028185%2Fphoto%2F4%3A%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20December%202024%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orfonline.org%2Fresearch%2Ffinancial-and-policy-catalysts-for-climate-tech-expansion-in-india-insights-from-the-green-innovation-and-investment-dialogue%23_edn30%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EObserver%20Research%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ORF)%20stated%20that%20of%20over%202%2C600%20registered%20climate%20tech%20startups%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20only%20about%20800%20are%20active.%20Of%20these%20800%20startups%2C%20only%2025%25%20have%20secured%20funding%2C%20mainly%20in%20the%20seed%20stage%2C%20with%20only%202.5%25%20reaching%20growth-stage%20capital%2C%20mostly%20in%20electric%20mobility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20is%20it%20important%20for%20India%20to%20fund%20climate%20tech%20startups%3F%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Gopalika%20Arora%2C%20an%20Associate%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Economy%20and%20Growth%20at%20ORF%2C%20notes%20that%20climate%20tech%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20bid%20to%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClimate%20tech%20plays%20a%20very%20critical%20role%2C%20not%20just%20in%20reducing%20emissions%2C%20but%20also%20in%20reshaping%20how%20these%20energy%20systems%20work.%20We%20are%20seeing%20a%20surge%20in%20climate%20tech%20startups%20and%20the%20growing%20ecosystem%20around%20them%2C%20which%20is%20very%20encouraging.%20This%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20foster%20innovation%2C%20promote%20market%20competition%2C%20and%20create%20jobs%20while%20addressing%20deeper%20societal%20challenges.%20In%20a%20developing%20economy%20like%20ours%2C%20this%20makes%20the%20energy%20transition%20not%20just%20greener%20but%20also%20more%20inclusive%20and%20people-positive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMismatch%20in%20investor%20expectations%20and%20startup%20needs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20circumstances%2C%20it%20begs%20the%20question%20of%20why%20climate%20tech%20startups%20aren%E2%80%99t%20receiving%20adequate%20and%20long-term%20funding.%20For%20starters%2C%20climate%20tech%20startups%20are%20tough%20businesses%20to%20build.%20They%20are%20very%20capital-intensive%2C%20and%20they%20also%20take%20time%20to%20show%20results.%20Most%20of%20them%20engage%20in%20serious%20investment%20in%20research%20and%20development%20and%20hardware%20just%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20laboratory%20and%20into%20the%20real%20world%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20electric%20vehicles%20or%20batteries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGopalika%20argues%20that%20these%20solutions%20demand%20heavy%20upfront%20spending%2C%20and%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20early-stage%20funding%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20seed%20and%20pre-Series%20A%20levels%2C%20has%20become%20more%20accessible%20thanks%20to%20a%20group%20of%20early%20investors%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20take%20a%20bet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20crunch%20hits%20when%20these%20companies%20try%20to%20scale.%20So%2C%20raising%20money%20on%20Series%20A%20is%20still%20a%20steep%20climb%2C%20and%20without%20that%20capital%2C%20many%20promising%20ventures%2