nderstand%20that%20you%20may%20not%20last%20without%20money%2C%20you%20may%20not%20scale%20up%20without%20money%2C%20but%20we%20had%20a%20different%20belief%20that%20we%20will%20work%20on%20impact.%20But%20what%20you%20see%20today%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20patient%20capital%2C%20which%20will%20align%20with%20a%20startup%E2%80%99s%20goal%20of%20impact%20and%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gautam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oorjan%20Cleantech%20has%20helped%20commercial%20spaces%20like%20the%20Mall%20of%20Dehradun%20adopt%20rooftop%20solar%2C%20despite%20challenges%20in%20securing%20long-term%20investment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-434298%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2262