a.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165925.451_11zon-1747654182-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165925.451_11zon-1747654182-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165925.451_11zon-1747654182-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-434310%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPolicy%20support%2C%20inclusive%20regulation%2C%20and%20innovation-friendly%20IP%20laws%20can%20empower%20women%20and%20underrepresented%20leaders%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20tech%20ecosystem.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20the%20most%20significant%20challenge%20lies%20in%20the%20transition%20from%20innovation%20to%20implementation.%20While%20India%20has%20no%20shortage%20of%20promising%20ideas%20ranging%20from%20EV%20infrastructure%20to%20AI-powered%20agriculture%20and%20carbon%20capture%20technologies%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20often%20missing%20is%20the%20support%20system%20to%20test%20these%20solutions%20at%20scale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20gap%20between%20lab-ready%20prototypes%20and%20market-ready%20products%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20parts%20of%20the%20innovation%20journey%20because%20the%20ecosystem%20for%20piloting%20and%20demonstrating%20new%20technologies%20in%20India%20is%20still%20developing.%20Many%20climate-tech%20ventures%20with%20innovative%20ideas%20struggle%20to%20find%20the%20infrastructure%20and%20partnerships%20needed%20to%20validate%20their%20solutions%20in%20real-world%20conditions%2C%20which%20is%20very%20crucial%20for%20building%20investor%20confidence%20and%20scaling%20their%20technologies%20effectively.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20India%20has%20institutions%20like%20the%20IIT%20Madras%20Research%20Park