data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286bf63fd-2df7-433d-a215-b40257da5840%5C%22%3E1.%20Nvidia's%20new%20office%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20about%20Nvidia's%20new%20office%20in%20Taiwan%20has%20been%20brewing%20since%20Huang%20said%20in%20January%20that%20the%20company's%20current%20building%20was%20too%20small%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Blooking%20for%20real%20estate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Taipei's%20mayor%2C%20Chiang%20Wan-an%2C%20generated%20buzz%20when%20he%20showed%20up%20at%20Huang's%20keynote.%20Huang%20went%20on%20to%20announce%20that%20Nvidia%20is%20eying%20the%20Beitou%20Shilin%20area%20%E2%80%94%20home%20to%20a%20science%20park%20%E2%80%94%20in%20northern%20Taipei%20for%20the%20tech%20giant's%20new%20Taiwan%20office%2C%20named%20%26quot%3BNvidia%20Constellation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20was%20met%20with%20applause%20and%20cheers%20from%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChiang%20said%20in%20a%20media%20interview%20following%20Huang's%20keynote%20that%20the%20city%20government%20welcomes%20Nvidia's%20move%20and%20will%20provide%20any%20necessary%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f06ac42-a7fd-4934-9b95-5caaaf37a448%5C%22%3E2.%20New%20computer%20systems%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20introduced%20Nvidia's%20DGX%20systems%2C%20which%20are%20designed%20for%20users%20who%20want%20heavy-duty%20AI%20without%20dedicating%20significant%20storage%20space%20to%20a%20weighty%20server%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20physical%20workstation%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20single%20computer%20or%20as%20a%20central%20node%20for%20multiple%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20computer%20is%20the%20most%20performance%20you%20can%20possibly%20get%20out%20of%20a%20wall%20socket.%20You%20could%20put%20this%20in%20your%20kitchen.%20But%20just%20barely%2C%20if%20you%20put%20this%20in%20your%20kitchen%20and%20then%20somebody%20runs%20the%20microwave%2C%20I%20think%20that's%20the%20limit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHua