on%20West%20in%20Orlando%2C%20Florida.%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680e8cf9c6ad288d147f44c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHorizon%20West%20offers%20housing%20options%20at%20various%20price%20points.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nicole%20Mickle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHorizon%20West%20has%20various%20housing%20options%20at%20different%20price%20points%2C%20which%20the%20developers%20specified%20in%20the%20master%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApartments%20could%20be%20around%20%242%2C500%20a%20month%2C%20and%20homes%20could%20be%20multimillion-dollar%20over%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Mickle%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20homes%20are%20still%20affordable%20for%20what%20Horizon%20West%20offers.%20You%20can't%20find%20this%20in%20other%20areas%20of%20Orlando%20at%20the%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfc1adca-d20d-449b-9d45-e840f17051b0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisney%20moves%20in%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMickle%20said%20the%20recent%20population%20boom%2C%20in%20tandem%20with%20residents'%20passion%20for%20Horizon%20West%2C%20could%20explain%20the%20stir%20around%20the%20Disney-backed%20housing%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20some%20want%20to%20do%20is%20keep%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Mickle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResidents%20circulated%20a%20petition%20last%20year%20saying%20they%20%26quot%3Bstrongly%20opposed%26quot%3B%20the%20construction%20because%20it%20threatened%20%26quot%3Bthe%20local%20environment%20and%20quality%20of%20life%20due%20to%20the%20inappropriate%20location%20and%20lack%20of%20adequate%20infrastructure.%26quot%3B%20Some%20residents%20told%20local%20media%20outlets%20that%20the%20housing%20units%20would%20bring%20more%20traffic%20to%20the%20area%2C%20while%20others%20wondered%20how%20affordable%20the%20units%20would%20actually%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20units%20