nd-scenes-us-air-force-collaborative-aircraft-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFury%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20be%20built%20from%20commercial%20parts%20to%20make%20manufacturing%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tried%20to%20eliminate%20really%20every%20bottleneck%20we%20could%20find%20around%20what%20makes%20an%20aircraft%20hard%20to%20produce%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schimpf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchimpf%20said%20the%20Fury's%20designers%2C%20for%20example%2C%20chose%20to%20go%20with%20a%20commercial%20business%20jet%20engine%20instead%20of%20a%20military%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Warzone%20reported%20in%202023%20that%20the%20Fury%20was%20designed%20with%20a%20Williams%20International%20FJ44-4M%20turbofan%20engine%2C%20which%20is%20popular%20in%20light%20business%20jets%20such%20as%20those%20in%20the%20Cessna%20Citation%20Series.%20Anduril%20didn't%20say%20in%20the%20Sunday%20CBS%20segment%20if%20the%20Fury%20still%20uses%20the%20same%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchimpf%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Fury%20avoids%20%26quot%3Bvery%20exquisite%2C%20big%20aircraft%20landing%20gear%26quot%3B%20in%20favor%20of%20a%20simpler%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20designed%20it%20so%20that%20it%20can%20be%20built%20in%20any%20machine%20shop%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20landing%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20designed%20nearly%20every%20part%20of%20this%20that%20can%20be%20made%20in%20hundreds%20of%20different%20places%20within%20the%20US%20from%20lots%20of%20different%20suppliers%2C%26quot%3B%20Schimpf%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fury%2C%20designated%20YFQ-44A%20by%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20is%20Anduril's%20bid%20to%20win%20the%20Pentagon's%20Collaborative%20Combat%20Aircraft%20contract%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20build%20large%20autonomous%20or%20semi-autonomous%20drones%20that%20can%20fly%20in%20tandem%20with%20piloted%20advanced%20fighter%20jets%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ff47-ngad-6th-generation-stealth-fighter-jet-concept-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENext%20Generation%20Air%20Dominance.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20service%20wants%20these%20new%20aircraft%20to%20be%20much%20cheaper%20than%20regular%20fighter%20jets.%20Gen.%20David%20Allvin%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20Chief%20of%20Staff%2C%20said%20in%20November%20that%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20drone%20wingman%20program%20was%20to%20bring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-run-out-ammo-weeks-china-national-defense-strategy-commission-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Baffordable%20mass%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20aerial%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20priority%20that%20reflects%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-invasion-west-focused-too-much-weapon-quantity-over-numbers-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emounting%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20that%20the%20American%20military%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-run-out-ammo-weeks-china-national-defense-strategy-commission-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erun%20out%20of%20weapons%20and%20ammo%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks%20or%20even%20days%20if%20it%20were%20to%20go%20to%20war%20with%20a%20rival%20such%20as%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20says%20the%20drone%20wingman%20program%20is%20a%20core%20part%20of%20its%20mandate%20to%20recalibrate%20itself%20for%20near-peer%20conflict.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrank%20Kendall%2C%20who%20served%20as%20Air%20Force%20Secretary%20until%20January%2C%20said%20he'd%20accelerated%20plans%20to%20develop%20Collaborative%20Combat%20Aircraft%20when%20analyses%20showed%20the%20drones%20would%20%26quot%3Bchange%20air%20warfare%20in%20some%20very%20fundamental%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnduril%20was%20one%20of%20two%20contractors%20selected%20to%20be%20the%20drone%20project's%20lead%20in%20April%202024%2C%20meaning%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5